data.description: Location, Location!!! Brookwood School District. With NO HOA. This 4 bd, 2.5 Bath, with over 3,300+ sqft.  Offers a big finished basement, with lots of additional rooms space to recreate anything in mind, to suit your needs. With a backyard this big and fully Fenced, you can have that outdoor dream space you've always wished for, NOT having to worry for any HOA approvals. This home also offers original hardwood floors. Recently updated waterproof kitchen flooring, stainless steel appliances, Fresh paint and updated carpet in all 4 rooms upstairs. This home has so much to offer. Conveniently located to lots of shops, restaurants and entertainment, this Home is also close to The Weeb Gin shops on Scenic Hwy 124 and Ronal Reagan Pkwy. Don't forget, that's in the Brookwood school district. Its a great starter home, ready to be cherished by any family or can also be a great investment opportunity to add to your portfolio. Property is currently Owner occupied. Please schedule 1-2 hrs in advance through showtime for approval.
